name: Hands in the Air
description:
Hands in the Air


“time capsule” is a series of datamoshed video journal entries of moments, memories & mysteries.

A visual poetic escape into the here & now -- a simple reminder to find moments to unplug from the metaverse & digital world and be still, be present.

This is a collection of 9 video entries from 2017-2021.
Artist: Jimmie Flora
Website: https://tell.ie/unrealityoftime
